(2, 'Cook & Create', 'cook-create', 'A fast-paced creative challenge where teams collaborate to build something unique under constraints.<br><br><span data-buffer=\"&lt;!--(figma)(/figma)--&gt;\"></span><ul role=\"list\"><li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Secret ingredient-based activity</li><li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Step-by-step collaborative creation</li><li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Limited actions per player for balanced participation</li><li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Fun, unpredictable, and creative outcomes</li></ul><span data-metadata=\"&lt;!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiZU1ZNnpzSHZwdjFuanR0WEVnYzk2ciIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjEyNjUzNDcwOTUsImRhdGFUeXBlIjoic2NlbmUiLCJlbnZpcm9ubWVudCI6Ind3dy5maWdtYS5jb20iLCJzZWxlY3RlZE5vZGVEYXRhIjoiMzM5MjoxMDE2fDMxfDAifQo=(/figmeta)--&gt;\"></span><span data-buffer=\"&lt;!--(figma)(/figma)--&gt;\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Encourages creativity, quick thinking, and seamless team coordination in a playful setting.</span>', 'activities/n3usT15oXiq8EqxdOr7QodV5yLkTsZI258AITCZr.png', 'activities/icons/12d6TowOlOVTqwPiSpdEHG5PN02Bzz50ebXLBDdK.png', 'active', 900, 15, 1500, 300, 120, 600, 120, 5, 5, 5, 100, 50, 20, -10, -15, 1, 3, 420, 30, '2026-05-31 16:09:58', '2026-06-02 15:20:36');

